---
// Bio component
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
			<!-- Text Content -->
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="animate-fade-in-left">
					<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
						About Me
					</h2>
					<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
					<p class="animate-fade-in-left animation-delay-200">
						I'm a passionate Software & AI Engineer with over 5 years of experience building intelligent systems and scalable applications. My journey began with a fascination for how machines can learn and adapt, which led me to specialize in machine learning, natural language processing, and full-stack development.
					</p>
					
					<p class="animate-fade-in-left animation-delay-400">
						Currently, I work at <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">TechCorp AI</span>, where I lead the development of AI-powered products that serve millions of users. I'm particularly interested in the intersection of AI and human-computer interaction, creating systems that are not only intelligent but also intuitive and accessible.
					</p>
					
					<p class="animate-fade-in-left animation-delay-600">
						When I'm not coding, you'll find me contributing to open-source projects, writing technical blog posts, or exploring the latest developments in AI research. I believe in the power of technology to solve real-world problems and make a positive impact on society.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Stats -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-8 animate-fade-in-left animation-delay-800">
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">5+</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Years Experience</div>
					</div>
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">50+</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Projects Completed</div>
					</div>
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">15+</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Technologies</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Image/Visual -->
			<div class="relative animate-fade-in-right">
				<div class="relative z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white shadow-2xl">
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
							<span class="font-medium">Currently Working On</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">AI-Powered Analytics Platform</h3>
						<p class="text-blue-100">
							Building a next-generation analytics platform that uses machine learning to provide actionable insights from complex data sets.
						</p>
						<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-4">
							<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">Python</span>
							<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">TensorFlow</span>
							<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">React</span>
							<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">AWS</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Decorative elements -->
				<div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full opacity-80"></div>
				<div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-6 h-6 bg-pink-400 rounded-full opacity-80"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	@keyframes fade-in-left {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateX(-30px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateX(0);
		}
	}
	
	@keyframes fade-in-right {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateX(30px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateX(0);
		}
	}
	
	.animate-fade-in-left {
		animation: fade-in-left 0.8s ease-out forwards;
	}
	
	.animate-fade-in-right {
		animation: fade-in-right 0.8s ease-out forwards;
	}
	
	.animation-delay-200 {
		animation-delay: 0.2s;
	}
	
	.animation-delay-400 {
		animation-delay: 0.4s;
	}
	
	.animation-delay-600 {
		animation-delay: 0.6s;
	}
	
	.animation-delay-800 {
		animation-delay: 0.8s;
	}
</style> 